<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Password Expired Notification</title>
</head>
<!-- justin waz here -->
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #C0392B; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 24px; margin: 0;">
                {{ sub_email_branding.admin_team_name }}
              </h1>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Body -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px;">
              <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0;">
                Hullo <strong>{{ display_name }}</strong>,
              </p>

              <p style="font-size: 16px;">
                Our records show that your <strong>{{ sub_email_branding.company_name }} domain password has expired</strong>. To regain access, please follow the steps below:
              </p>

              <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 20px 0;" />

              <!-- Section 1 -->
              <h2 style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #C0392B;">1. Visit a {{ sub_email_branding.company_name }} Office ({{ sub_email_branding.office_locations }})</h2>
              <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0;">
                You must be physically present at one of our offices ({{ sub_email_branding.office_locations }}) to reset an expired password.
              </p>

              <!-- Section 2 -->
              <h2 style="font-size: 18px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #C0392B;">2. Plug Your PC Directly into the LAN</h2>
              <ol style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Lock</strong> or log out of your computer.
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Connect an Ethernet cable</strong> from your PC to the corporate LAN port (no Wi-Fi).
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Do not attempt to log in yet.</strong> Wait for the network link to establish (about 30–60 seconds).
                </li>
              </ol>

              <!-- Section 3 -->
              <h2 style="font-size: 18px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #C0392B;">3. Wait for Propagation</h2>
              <p style="font-size: 16px;">
                Allow 1–2 minutes for your account status to update on the network. During this time, please refrain from attempting to log in.
              </p>

              <!-- Section 4 -->
              <h2 style="font-size: 18px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #C0392B;">4. Log In and Change Password</h2>
              <ol style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Press Ctrl + Alt + Del</strong> and log in with your <strong>expired password</strong>.
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  You should see a prompt to change your password.
                  Enter your expired password as the “Old Password,” then choose a new password that meets the requirements below.
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Click OK</strong> to finalize your new password and return to your desktop.
                </li>
              </ol>

              <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px;">
                <strong>If you do not see a change-password prompt after 2 minutes:</strong>
                <ul style="margin: 5px 0 10px 20px;">
                  <li>Confirm your PC is still plugged directly into the LAN (no Wi-Fi).</li>
                  <li>If the prompt still does not appear, please ask a {{ sub_email_branding.admin_person_title }} for assistance.</li>
                </ul>
              </p>

              <!-- Password Requirements -->
              <h2 style="font-size: 18px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #C0392B;">5. New Password Requirements</h2>
              <ul style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Length:</strong> At least 8 characters</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
                  <strong>Character Groups:</strong> Must include at least three of:
                  <ul style="margin: 5px 0 5px 20px;">
                    <li>Uppercase letters (A–Z)</li>
                    <li>Lowercase letters (a–z)</li>
                    <li>Numbers (0–9)</li>
                    <li>Symbols (e.g., <code>! @ # $ % ^ &amp; *</code>)</li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>History:</strong> Cannot match any of your last 24 passwords</li>
                <li><strong>Username Exclusion:</strong> Cannot contain sequences of three or more characters from your username</li>
              </ul>

              <p style="font-size: 16px;">
                If you need any further assistance, please contact {{ sub_email_branding.admin_team_name }} at
                <a href="mailto:{{ sub_email_branding.admin_email }}" style="color: #C0392B;">{{ sub_email_branding.admin_email }}</a>.
              </p>

              <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 0;">
                Thank you,<br />
                <strong>{{ sub_email_branding.admin_team_name }}</strong><br />
                <a href="mailto:{{ sub_email_branding.admin_email }}" style="color: #C0392B;">{{ sub_email_branding.admin_email }}</a><br />
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #ecf0f1; text-align: center; padding: 12px; font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
              &copy; {{ lookup('pipe','date +%Y') }} {{ sub_email_branding.company_brand }} — All rights reserved.
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
